{"tid":257010,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[A/I]Clash of Clan CoC新手老手clan, 一GAME 2玩玩","createTime":"2017-05-25T02:21:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-26T00:20:38.000Z","uid":91424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fef7be89fd97d96f1311964f44056376e4632175","tid":257010,"uid":91424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T02:21:55.000Z","msg":"最新更新 1game 2玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"color: maroon;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">高登仔新手俱樂部 [HKG] </span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">Search 「高登仔新手」就會搵到個clan  </span><br />\n主要培育新手，clan war其次<br />\n走輕鬆向<br />\n唔會chur住大家玩<br />\n有10本~8本捐兵比新手<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n簡單clan規:<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: green;\">申請入會時，請附帶一句中文或港式英文</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2.捐兵比例1:4,即收4兵，請捐返最少1兵(6本或以下者，不受此規限)<br />\n3.逢周未(正式場)clan war 請出兵最少1場，不求成績，只求盡力<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: purple;\">weekday clan war是練習場，主要供大家練習打cw，及解成就。出唔出兵，點樣打，都無所謂，悉隨尊便。</span><br />\n5.請勿無故缺席2星期正式場，否則以死魚方式處理。<br />\n6.定期清理死魚，留返個位比有需要既朋友<br />\n7.請積極參與，活躍討論，定期上水，多作交流。<br />\n8.<span style=\"color: navy;\">雖然個名叫高登仔，但歡迎非高登仔/CD rom加入</span><br />\n9.<span style=\"color: red;\">本clan以人話(正體中文)為主，謝絕5p字，火星字及殘體字等，非人類語言</span><br />\n10. 已有whatsapp group,方便交流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歡迎加入coc大家庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nHappy gaming<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"930ba82f880de82c44c80c67e6ef3150e1b54b66","tid":257010,"uid":35706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T05:41:41.000Z","msg":"新down 左, 點先入到clan?"},{"pid":"7b0278ad18db661838679b66c62fa28848e3a573","tid":257010